manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Description Little Whispers Food Feeder Pacifiers are the perfect way to introduce solid foods to your precious baby. Made with high quality, safety complaint materials, you can have comfort in using these fun feeders for both food introductions and teething relief. Simply add the food of your choice to the silicone nipple, lock it closed, then sit back and watch your baby discover the world of flavours. These pacifiers work great with fruits, vegetables, meat, purées, frozen breastmilk, and much more. The small holes in the silicone nipples allow juices to pass through, without the risk of choking. Encouraging self feeding and promoting independence, we know your baby will love the experience these pacifiers provide!

reviews.reviewText: This is awesome to use when the baby starts teething! This sooths the gums while providing a cold, healthy option for the baby to gnaw on when the gums ache. It is easy to prepare and clean. Little fingerts are able to hold onto the pacifier and learn to manipulate the pacifier.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for baby
reviews.reviewText: My 8mo daughter has been enjoying her food journey so far and I’m always on the lookout to feed her in different ways. I’ve seen these online and wanted to try them for my baby since she’s ready to eat on her own. Although she’s eating food, I am still wary about choking. I love these for fruit and veggies. I do chop/cut them up well so she is able to slowly eat it on her own. They are the perfect size for her to grab and for her mouth to chew. Very easy to clean as well. They do stain but only with certain foods like steamed carrots. Strawberries and blueberries seemed to work best so far.
